      "date": "2013-04-23 16:57:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi Vitaly, what's wrong with the original fix of LU-481, i.e., what makes you think this fix is not good?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
